    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Yes that's it, it's just that I do have the feeling that this will annoy bootstrap users to have to provide a template for everything while providing the option would ease their lives a lot.\n\nLet's see how the first CSE and integrators are going to use the library. Then we will see if that's really a need.\n",
